## Claim Boundary

- `paper_claim_positive`: full required metrics beat the best strong baseline and are non-worse than no-process.
- `route_guard_positive`: useful negative-transfer guard evidence, but not a strong-baseline paper claim.
- `incomplete_metric`: at least one required metric is missing; rerun metric extraction before a full claim.
- Source-inversion / registered source-path branches remain diagnostic unless aligned scan-path data appears.


